CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777489866
OL,3,CUK economy set for #35bn hit from
OL,4,CMiddle East energy crisis, think tank
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Middle East energy shock could
OL,8,Fwipe around #35 billion from the UK
OL,9,Feconomy over the next two years in a
OL,10,F"best-case" scenario, an economic
OL,11,Fthink tank has warned.
OL,13,FThe National Institute of Economic and
OL,14,FSocial Research (Niesr) said that a
OL,15,Fmore protracted crisis in the Middle
OL,16,FEast could see the UK enter a
OL,17,Frecession in the second half this year.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
